name: HazioSanFranciscoAirQualityFlashBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
This skill is designed to give you a quick overview of the air quality in San Francisco. The air quality data is obtained from the EPA's AirNow website which updates the air quality daily, so the information in the skill is always up to date. For more information about this skill, visit www.hazio.co.

An example of what Alexa could say when playing this skill is "the air quality in San Francisco is currently good, a 42 on the air quality index."

This skill was made as part of an environmental service project begun by 3 students at Pacific Bay Christian School in Pacifica, California.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
